name: RemoteConfigEventData

versionNumber.description: The version number of the version's corresponding Remote Config template.

updateTime.description: When the Remote Config template was written to the Remote Config server.

updateUser.description: Aggregation of all metadata fields about the account that performed the update.

description.description: The user-provided description of the corresponding Remote Config template.

updateType.description: What type of update was made.

Only present if this version is the result of a rollback, and will be the
 version number of the Remote Config template that was rolled-back to.

description: The data within all Firebase Remote Config events.
